name: IELTS Speaking 1
instructions:
• You will have to talk about the topic for 1 to 2 minutes.
  • You have one minute to think about what you’re going to say.
  • You can make some notes to help you if you wish.

category.name: IELTS
category.description: The International English Language Testing System, or IELTS™, is an international standardised test of English language proficiency for non-native English language speakers. It is jointly managed by the British Council, IDP: IELTS Australia and Cambridge Assessment English, and was established in 1989.
